931
01:04:04,307 --> 01:04:07,276
Not exactly. I put him
in the freezer because...

932
01:04:08,978 --> 01:04:11,572
It's another story.
You don't need to hear it.

933
01:04:18,654 --> 01:04:22,181
For 20 years,
I've rotted my life away

934
01:04:22,291 --> 01:04:24,316
with lowlifes and scumbags.

935
01:04:24,427 --> 01:04:28,420
And you cheated me
out of my salvation!

936
01:04:28,531 --> 01:04:30,226
Look, you have your freedom,

937
01:04:30,333 --> 01:04:33,234
the sky, the trees,
the scent of the earth.

938
01:04:33,336 --> 01:04:34,894
Money can't buy that.

939
01:04:35,004 --> 01:04:38,872
So you thought you
could escape me by dying.

940
01:04:40,576 --> 01:04:43,010
I don't think that was his plan.

941
01:04:43,112 --> 01:04:45,603
He thought he'd
be safe from me in hell.

942
01:04:45,715 --> 01:04:49,242
Well, he made a big mistake.

943
01:04:49,352 --> 01:04:51,946
Here I come,
you son of a bitch.

944
01:04:52,054 --> 01:04:53,783
No!

945
01:04:57,193 --> 01:04:59,491
How could you do this to me?

946
01:04:59,595 --> 01:05:03,190
What's wrong with you people?

947
01:05:03,299 --> 01:05:05,859
