948
01:05:05,968 --> 01:05:08,163
L... what, uh!

949
01:05:36,666 --> 01:05:39,066
God bless this soul
and take him to your kingdom.

950
01:05:39,168 --> 01:05:40,465
You know the rest.

951
01:06:20,977 --> 01:06:24,413
