to business.

972
01:07:30,413 --> 01:07:33,405
- Is Roseanna at the hospital?
- I don't think so.

973
01:07:33,516 --> 01:07:36,110
When she gets back, tell her
I'm going to be late tonight.

974
01:07:36,218 --> 01:07:38,812
