977
01:08:13,589 --> 01:08:15,614
Marcello.
Marcello Beatto.

978
01:08:15,724 --> 01:08:17,021
Who's that?

979
01:08:17,126 --> 01:08:19,424
Francesca. Remember me?

980
01:08:19,528 --> 01:08:21,860
Of course I remember you.

981
01:08:21,964 --> 01:08:23,363
